      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.832 - Al-Mu'alla ibn Khunays asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about praying on qufr (bare ground or desert soil) and qīr (a type of tar or pitch).\nImam (as) said: \"There is no issue with it”."
